      "coverage": "gaps",
      "gaps": [
        "CRITICAL: No latency histogram — cannot measure p50/p95/p99, cannot verify SLA compliance, cannot alert on latency regression. Add request_duration_seconds histogram with buckets tuned around the 10s SLA (e.g., 0.1, 0.5, 1, 2, 5, 10, 15, 30)",
