    "circuit_breakers": "None present. This is a significant gap — sustained S3 degradation will cascade into service-wide resource exhaustion.",
    "graceful_degradation": "No degradation strategy. Consider: returning a 503 with Retry-After header when circuit breaker is open, or accepting uploads to a local queue for async retry if S3 is down."
  },

