      "reason": "The service has a defined SLA (99% of uploads within 10s) but no latency histogram or summary metric to measure it. Without this, there is no way to alert on SLA breach, report compliance, or detect latency regression. This is the single most critical gap — you cannot manage what you cannot measure.",
